snippet.textDisplay:
Some tips on the second part of the game... Not that you did bad, I think you did pretty well :)
If Baldi spots you, prioritize finding safe rooms. Baldi can't get you in there. (A safe room has "safe room" written on the door). I suggest once getting to the safe room, use that time to refill your stamina, and to wait for Baldi to get further away from you so he isn't camping your door. 
Took me a few tries, but this is what helped me the most. 
Just some info for if you wanna give it another go :)
